quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,49,"[O Muḥammad], inform My servants that it is I who am the Forgiving, the Merciful,"
  15,50,"And that it is My punishment which is the painful punishment."
  15,51,"And inform them about the guests of Abraham,"
  16,28,"The ones whom the angels take in death [while] wronging themselves,{1} and [who] then offer submission, [saying], ",footnotes:1:i.e., having made punishment due to them for their numerous sins and crimes.
  16,29,"So enter the gates of Hell to abide eternally therein, and how wretched is the residence of the arrogant."
  16,30,"And it will be said to those who feared Allāh, "